snippet.title: Gallop Racer 2006 Journey to the Field of Legends EP 1
snippet.description:
Journey to the Field of Legends: With this episode, we're focusing on the debut of a new horse I've bred Called Gold Dust. This Horse has shown a lot of promise and I've enjoyed racing him. Maybe I'll use him for the Field of Legends

If you guys have any tips or see me doing something wrong please don't hesitate to comment below and let me know. Even though these games are still over 20 years old we are still finding out new things about them every day.

Thank you for watching and also a big shoutout to the Horse racing community because without them this wouldn't have been possible.

#Gallopracer2006 #Gallopracer
